  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8301692/" class="title-link">做了厨子后觉得比较重要的</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8301692"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/alsdlt/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u52709166-33.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/alsdlt/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">alsdlt</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-01-20"
      class="main-meta">2017-01-20 00:41:40</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8301692_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  季节不断变化，不同种类的鱼贝也相应上市。不仅是人气导致原料鱼越来越难买到，气候变迁等原因也使得鱼的巡游环境发生改变。不是说一定要选择名产地的鱼贝，而是要寻找能够让自己发自内心认可的鱼。金枪鱼也好，鲣鱼也罢，优质的鱼类越来越少，而大的不可思议的鲍鱼却十分低廉...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            中国民族摄影艺术出版社2015版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
